# Blockquotes Examples in Zolt

## Basic Blockquotes

Simple quote using `>`:

> This is a simple blockquote.
> It can span multiple lines.

## Blockquotes with Attributes

Styled quotes:

> This quote has an ID{#quote1}
> This quote is red{color=red}
> This quote is highlighted{#quote3 background=yellow}

## Nested Blockquotes

Quotes within quotes:

> Level 1 quote
>
> > Level 2 quote
> >
> > > Level 3 quote
> >
> > Back to level 2
>
> Back to level 1

## Blockquotes vs Inline Styling

> This is an entire blockquote paragraph.
> All lines are styled the same way.

This is a paragraph with ||inline styled text||{color=blue} inside.

